Goiter is one of the medical issues that is affecting lots of people all over the world because they lack some basic nutrients in their daily meals or due to health conditions. According to healthline, there are some basic causes of goiter that every person needs to know and in this article, I will educate you on some of these major causes.
1. The first cause of goiter in most people around the world can be pregnancy. If you are pregnant, your body may produce hormones that cause your thyroid or goiter to expand but it is not a cancerous health condition that you should be afraid of.
2. Another major cause of goiter in many people around the world is thyroid cancer. If you are a victim of thyroid cancer, one side of your neck or thyroid will expand. So, you are advised to visit your doctor regularly for a proper medical check-up and treatment.
3. One of the major causes of goiter in most people can be due to Graves disease which is one of the health conditions in which your thyroid secretes excess hormones than normal. So, it is recommended that you visit your doctor for a regular medical checkup and treatment before it is too late.


